OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1774271469
OL,3,CScotland bans greyhound racing
OL,5,FScotland has become the second country
OL,6,Fin the UK to ban greyhound racing in
OL,7,Fjust over 24 hours as MSPs backed a
OL,8,FBill to end the sport.
OL,10,FThe Greyhound Racing (Offences)
OL,11,F(Scotland) Bill was supported by 70
OL,12,Fvotes to 27 at Stage Three, with 19
OL,13,Fabstentions.
OL,15,FWednesday's vote at Holyrood comes
OL,16,Fafter the Senedd in Wales voted on
OL,17,FTuesday to ban the sport in a move
OL,18,Fhailed by campaigners as a "landmark
OL,19,Fmoment for dog welfare".
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
