FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1774271469
OL,3,CScotland bans greyhound racing
OL,5,FIt will make it an offence to operate
OL,6,Fa racing track for greyhounds and for
OL,7,Fa dog owner to race their animal on
OL,8,Fone.
OL,10,FThe south of Scotland had a history of
OL,11,Fstaging greyhound races until 2017,
OL,12,Fwhen the Halcrow Stadium in Gretna
OL,13,Fclosed its gates.
OL,15,FIn Hawick, the Hawick Target Hill
OL,16,FGreyhound Track was open between 1939
OL,17,Fand 1967, while Albert Park, home of
OL,18,FHawick Royal Albert Football Club
OL,19,Fstaged greyhound races between 1989
OL,20,Fand 1999.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1774271469
OL,3,CScotland bans greyhound racing
OL,5,FThere have been no greyhound racing
OL,6,Ftracks in all of Scotland since 2025,
OL,7,Fwhen the Thornton Stadium in Fife
OL,8,Fsuspended operations indefinitely.
OL,10,FGreen MSP for Mid Scotland and Fife
OL,11,FMark Ruskell brought forward the Bill.
OL,13,FMr Ruskell said: "I'm delighted that
OL,14,Fwe've got my member's Bill over the
OL,15,Fline and that we will finally end this
OL,16,Fcruel gambling-led sport in Scotland.
OL,18,F"Greyhound racing belongs in the past,
OL,19,Fand my Bill ensures that no more dogs
OL,20,Fwill be forced to endure it.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1774271469
OL,3,CScotland bans greyhound racing
OL,5,F"The case against greyhound racing has
OL,6,Fnever been stronger and the
OL,7,Finternational consensus to end the
OL,8,Fsuffering of these dogs is now
OL,9,Funstoppable."
OL,11,FMr Ruskell continued: "It has been
OL,12,Fdeeply personal for me. In 2015, my
OL,13,Ffamily rehomed an ex-racing greyhound
OL,14,Fcalled Bert. He sadly passed away last
OL,15,Fyear.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1774271469
OL,3,CScotland bans greyhound racing
OL,5,F"He was a wonderful dog, kind and
OL,6,Faffectionate and so patient with kids
OL,7,F` and even with cats ` but what I
OL,8,Fdidn't fully understand, until I
OL,9,Fstarted working on this campaign, was
OL,10,Fthe trauma that Bert had endured while
OL,11,Fracing."
OL,13,FEarlier this year Cumbrian greyhound
OL,14,Ftrainer Joe Edgar criticised proposals
OL,15,Fto ban the sport, insisting it is
OL,16,F"safe".
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1774271469
OL,3,CScotland bans greyhound racing
OL,5,FMr Edgar told ITV Border: "Welfare is
OL,6,Freally really important, we have to do
OL,7,Fthe best by our dogs, we have
OL,8,Finspections all the time, the dogs are
OL,9,Fwell cared for.
OL,11,F"It seems a bit silly to me really,
OL,12,Fthere's no tracks left in Scotland so
OL,13,Fwhat they're trying to ban doesn't
OL,14,Factually happen anyway."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
