OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1774271469
OL,3,CScotland bans greyhound racing
OL,5,FAnimal rights campaigners welcomed the
OL,6,Fpassing of the Bill, with a
OL,7,Fspokesperson for Say No To Greyhound
OL,8,FRacing in Scotland saying: "Since
OL,9,F2017, we've stood together as a
OL,10,Fgrassroots group, fighting tirelessly
OL,11,Fand successfully to stop a new track
OL,12,Fat Wallyford in East Lothian and to
OL,13,Fsecure a nationwide ban on greyhound
OL,14,Fracing in Scotland ` groundbreaking
OL,15,Flegislation that marks a historic step
OL,16,Fforward for animal welfare."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1774271469
OL,3,CScotland bans greyhound racing
OL,5,FOwen Sharp, chief executive of Dogs
OL,6,FTrust, said: "Tonight's announcement
OL,7,Fthat greyhound racing will be
OL,8,Fconsigned to the history books in
OL,9,FScotland is a landmark victory for dog
OL,10,Fwelfare.
OL,12,F"This incredible news comes just hours
OL,13,Fafter Wales also took decisive action
OL,14,Fto end greyhound racing ` two huge
OL,15,Fsteps towards ending the needless
OL,16,Fsuffering of greyhounds."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1774271469
OL,3,CScotland bans greyhound racing
OL,5,FGreyhound Board of Great Britain data
OL,6,Ffrom 2023 showed 109 dogs had died
OL,7,Ftrackside in the UK, an increase on
OL,8,Fdeaths in 2022, whole there were 4,238
OL,9,Finjuries in 2023.
OL,11,FWhile the Scottish Government
OL,12,Fsupported the Bill, the Scottish
OL,13,FConservatives and Scottish Labour were
OL,14,Fcritical of the move.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G9/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1774271469
OL,3,CScotland bans greyhound racing
OL,5,FTory MSP Finley Carson said: "It's got
OL,6,Fto be recognised that it's hard to
OL,7,Fconclude anything other than this
OL,8,Fprocess has been a waste of precious
OL,9,Fparliamentary time. Time that will not
OL,10,Fimprove the welfare of one single
OL,11,Fgreyhound in Scotland.
OL,13,F"There is no active track, there is no
OL,14,Fongoing racing, and yet we have been
OL,15,Fasked to pass a total ban without ever
OL,16,Fexploring the very thing that has
OL,17,Fimproved welfare in England and Wales
OL,18,F` licensing, robust legislation,
OL,19,Fregulation and proper oversight."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G10/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
