OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1774271469
OL,3,CScotland bans greyhound racing
OL,5,FScottish Labour MSP Rhoda Grant said:
OL,6,F"As this Bill stands, it does nothing
OL,7,Fto improve the welfare of any animal
OL,8,Fin Scotland.
OL,10,F"It will stop a novel greyhound
OL,11,Fracetrack being opened in Scotland,
OL,12,Fbut I don't think in any event that a
OL,13,Ftrack would have received planning
OL,14,Fpermission had it sought to open."
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
